* ATmega328p - Keypad Authentication with I2C LCD and RFID
* LCD: SDA → PC4, SCL → PC5 (I2C Address: 0x3F)
* Keypad on PCF8574 (I2C Address: 0x20)
* RFID: SS → PB2, RST → PD2
* Solenoid/Relay on PD4
* Exit Button on PB0
